title: Pakistan crush India in West Asia Baseball Cup semi-final - Sport - DAWN.COM
content:
LAHORE: Defending champions Pakistan crushed arch-rivals India 14-1 in the West Asia Baseball Cup semi-final at the Enghelab Stadium in Tehran on Tuesday.

Pakistan in the final will face Palestine on Wednesday.

Palestine in their last-four match defeated Iran 18-3.

Published in Dawn, May 21st, 2025
